 END--><br><br>Hmm, better ask this sneaky person hiding behind a giant mushroom.<br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www-rocq.inria.fr/~bnguyen/RV_Ainie.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <br><br>Damn and I thought I had friends. So I look a bit harder, and see an Ogre. Now this guy looked like he ate Hobbits for breakfast, so I decide to chance it. 'Sir Ogre, will you pledge your Primal Axe to the slaughtering of Hobbits? Will you be the Liberator of the Large?'<br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www-rocq.inria.fr/~bnguyen/RV_Dex.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br>Oh well, I guess it was worth a try.<br><br>Running a bit low on elite infantry, I decide to ask a well renoun Arch Mage to lend his elementals to the destruction of Rivervale.<br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www-rocq.inria.fr/~bnguyen/RV_Kryp.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br>It seems they were outfitted with the wrong sort of equipment I suppose.<br><br>...<br><br>Ok so it is just my Fiance and me. But then I remembered the person whose motto was the same as mine, the great Silene Starlyte! She accepted to join, yet as I was getting her in Kunark, I received terrible news...<br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www-rocq.inria.fr/~bnguyen/RV_Alt.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <br><br>Seems that seeing Rivervale too close was a sight enough to scare even the bravest of Barbarians ... /sigh<br><br><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  The writing gets shakier</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br><br>Silene and I enter Rivervale alone. So much for all the machos talking, I see how it comes when the going gets tough. On the road to the Mayor, we are engaged in a furious battle against the inhabitants of the Vale, including some well know terrorists such as Praxx the Rainmaker and Passe Partout. I'd love to give the whole report of the fight, I'll write more once this town is in ruins.<br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www-rocq.inria.fr/~bnguyen/RV_Fight.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  The page is stained with Elven blood</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br><br>Surrounded... Cornered... Maybe it was all a trap... I hope Silene will get away... Just the voices of these wretched Hobbits ringing out... <br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www-rocq.inria.fr/~bnguyen/RV_Malio.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br>Tunare Help me...<br><br><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  The writing ends here</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/uauroreakengro.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aurore Akengro</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/28/02 6:17:23 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/ulunarsexling.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lunar Sexling</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 34<br> <font color=#333333>(1/28/02 7:25:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fascension10244frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=489.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A page in a diary</span><hr size=1> i hope u die and the smalls make a tunic to fit all twelve of us halfling members out of u.. Great job malio, passe and praxx~  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/ucoltranehox.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ColtraneHoX</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 318<br> <font color=#333333>(1/28/02 7:28:04 pm)</font><br>   <a h